text:
This outfit,
we're all going to wear it at 283Pro, right?

Yeah...
It's going to be spectacular, isn't it...!

Mm-hmm... Everyone, huh?
It kind of feels like one big class, doesn't it?

Indeed...
It's going to be on that scale...!

Hey...
I'm really happy about it.

After graduating from high school, I thought I wouldn't get to
experience the feeling of being in a class or at school anymore.

Yeah, I get that...
But maybe we'll form even stronger bonds.

Because from now on,
Hana will be spending a lot of time at 283 Pro.

I want to love 283PRO even more,
and I'll work hard to be loved by everyone too.
